profile: 'JL Concrete was founded and is run by Justin Leppard, who has spent more than half of his life mastering his craft as an expert concrete finisher. Justin is passionate about the potential opportunities concrete presents to home owners and businesses, and he takes pride in leading these projects with the highest level of quality. When you decide to invest in a JL Concrete project, you can trust in the work that'll be provided. Service options include custom decorative overlays, driveways, porches, basement developments, decks and more.'
